    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior has several visible scuffs and some fading in the clear coat, while the interior shows its age with some staining on the upholstery and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new tires or a brake service. It's a solid, functional car that isn't perfect but still has plenty of life left in it.",
